<section class="py-16 px-6 lg:py-24">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-gray-900 mb-6">Resources for Sponsors</h1>

    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
      Thank you for supporting the 2025 DLF Forum! We’re excited to partner with you to create a welcoming, dynamic event. This page outlines essential information to help you prepare for the event and maximize your presence.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">🎪 Sponsor Table Information</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      Sponsor tables will be located in high-traffic areas near the conference registration desk and refreshment stations. Each sponsor table includes:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6">
      <li>One 6’ table and two chairs</li>
      <li>Electricity access (upon request)</li>
      <li>Wi-Fi access</li>
      <li>Optional signage provided by the sponsor</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">📦 Shipping & Materials</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      If you are shipping materials to the venue, please use the following address and clearly mark all boxes with your organization name and “DLF Forum Sponsor”:
    </p>
    <div class="bg-white border shadow-sm rounded-lg p-4 text-gray-800 mb-6">
      <p class="font-semibold">The Westin Denver Downtown<br>
      Attn: DLF Forum – Sponsor Table<br>
      1672 Lawrence Street<br>
      Denver, CO 80202</p>
    </div>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
      Materials should arrive no earlier than <strong>3 days prior</strong> to the event start. You are responsible for return shipping arrangements. The hotel staff can assist with outbound shipments at the concierge desk.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">🎤 Sponsor Participation Guidelines</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
      We encourage sponsor representatives to participate in the Forum as full attendees—engage in sessions, network, and be visible community members! Please note that while sponsor visibility is welcome, product pitches or sales messaging should be limited to your exhibit table.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">📣 Recognition and Promotion</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
      As a sponsor, your organization will be featured in:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 mb-6">
      <li>The official conference website</li>
      <li>Event signage and slide decks</li>
      <li>Social media shout-outs and acknowledgments</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
      If you haven’t already provided your logo or promotional copy, please send it to <a href="mailto:forum@diglib.org" class="underline text-blue-600">forum@diglib.org</a> by <strong>September 15, 2025</strong>.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-blue-gray-900 mt-10 mb-4">✉️ Questions?</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-700 mb-2">
      Reach out to the DLF Forum team at <a href="mailto:forum@diglib.org" class="underline text-blue-600">forum@diglib.org</a> with any questions about logistics, signage, or sponsorship benefits.
    </p>
